5:
Wow. You're going to have Alice pick
out a swimsuit for you, Primula?
8:
Nice. Maybe I'll try wearing
something revealing for a change,
too?
12:
U-um... We still haven't decided
whether it will be r-revealing or not...
17:
Paradise Isle... I can hardly wait! 
It's gonna be a blast!
21:
Yeah! The beach, the resort, the
casino... You don't usually get to
experience stuff like that as an
adventurer!
25:
I'll have fun to my heart's content
this time! Let's relax until we're totally
sick of it!
37:
Thanks for waiting! Soba, noodles,
grilled seafood, and today's
vegetable curry!
45: Looks like she can't stop working...
49:
Ahaha, Scott was in trouble, you
see? He opened a second store but
didn't have enough staff.
52:
When someone asks for help, well...
It's fun for me to do what I can!
55:
Yuna, you're a lifesaver! Thanks so
much!
And it's good to see you, Alk!
63:
Th-thank you for w-waiting. Here's
your g-grilled seafood...
67:
Th-thanks?! You're working here too,
Primula?
72:
She seemed interested, so I invited
her to come help out!
83:
Hey, you're playing restaurant owner
again this year? We came to check
it out.
86:
Welcome! Table for three? I'll show
you to your seats!
89:
...Well aren't you a sight for sore
eyes. Mind pouring me a drink?
93:
Thanks for the compliment! I'll bring
you a nice, cold bottle, so please
enjoy it amongst yourselves!
98:
Hey, babe with the dark hair! Come
here and chat a little, would you?
104:
You know? Pleasing your customers
isn't too big a thing to ask. That's
what girls are good at, right?
112:
What does her being a girl have to
do with anything?
116:
Nothing at all! Can't you tell that
you're upsetting Primula?
119:
Ha. Give me a break. She's begging
for my attention wearing an outfit
like that.
121:
My dad's on the board for Paradise
Isle, you know? Now be a good girl
and give me good customer service!
125:
Don't you DARE talk to Primula like
that!
132:
Hey, you hit me! She HIT me! I'm
gonna tell my dad, and he'll get this
whole place shut down!
135: I-I'm sorry! It's all my fault!
139:
You didn't do anything wrong,
Primula. I promise you that!
143: I'm going to go have a little chat.
151:
I'm not gonna let a little rat like him
get away with running his mouth like
that.
156:
Thanks, you guys! But we're going to
keep this discussion civil, all right?
161: You just knocked him on his ass!
166:
I'm... I'm so sorry! You have my most
sincere apologies for my son's
behavior!
174:
Gill... I had good intentions always
cleaning up after you, but I can see
now that I was making a mistake.
176:
Look at this young woman's courage
and initiativeshe did all this for a
friend! Don't you feel ANYTHING
when you see someone do
something so noble?!
179:
N-no, sir... I did overreact somewhat
to the situation...
182:
There's nothing to be ashamed of
with such a strong response. Your
straightforward spirit is highly
admirable, young lady.
185:
U-uh... I don't know about that?! 
I didn't really do anything special
190:
Y-You're amazing, Yuna! You're
strong, kind, and wonderful all
around!
199:
Hey, uh... What's the proper way to
react in this situation?! I'm kinda lost,
here!
202:
I can see you're a person worthy of
trust, and I have just one favor to
ask of you!
205:
Th-thank you for waiting...
Dammit, why am I doing this...
208:
Speak up, Gill! We can't hear you!
And don't forget to smile, smile,
smile!
212:
No need to be nervous. Just relax,
okay?
218:
Guess there isn't much for us to do,
hey?
221:
Well, you know. Yuna's pretty
self-sufficient.
225: Hello and welcome! Table for two?
